00:40:43.160 --> 00:40:44.480
tradition.

00:40:44.680 --> 00:40:48.840
They know what is Self-Realization.

00:40:49.040 --> 00:40:51.680
But in Russia

00:40:51.880 --> 00:40:55.960
where they never knew who is God.

00:40:56.160 --> 00:40:57.440
You won’t believe

00:40:57.640 --> 00:41:01.920
that I can’t hold a program on such a small scale there.

00:41:02.120 --> 00:41:08.840
Minimum of minimum, sixteen to eighteen thousand people,

00:41:09.040 --> 00:41:13.560
a very learned, very learned people.

00:41:13.760 --> 00:41:18.640
See, they are scientists and they are doctors.

00:41:18.840 --> 00:41:22.160
And the scientists - I started on

00:41:22.360 --> 00:41:24.760
science - they said, "Mother we know science, everything.

00:41:24.960 --> 00:41:27.400
Now we don’t want to know anymore science.

00:41:27.600 --> 00:41:30.400
You tell us why are we on this earth

00:41:30.600 --> 00:41:33.000
and you tell us about divine laws.

00:41:33.200 --> 00:41:37.680
We don’t want to hear any more about science, had enough of it."

00:41:37.880 --> 00:41:40.400
Can you imagine they have bestowed

00:41:40.600 --> 00:41:43.280
a very great honor on Me?

00:41:43.480 --> 00:41:45.960
St. Petersburg University.

00:41:46.160 --> 00:41:48.280
I don’t know if he has told you or not,

00:41:48.480 --> 00:41:49.960
but surprisingly,

00:41:50.160 --> 00:41:52.720
it's one of the oldest universities

00:41:52.920 --> 00:41:56.600
and there have been only ten members so far been

00:41:56.800 --> 00:41:59.480
and Einstein is one of them, you see.

00:41:59.680 --> 00:42:02.920
I said how, I felt very amazed, was...

00:42:03.120 --> 00:42:04.920
I felt very shy with the whole thing.

00:42:05.160 --> 00:42:08.040
They said, "Why Einstein? Einstein only worked on matter,

00:42:08.240 --> 00:42:10.200
you are working on human beings".

00:42:10.400 --> 00:42:13.760
I said, "I am not working; it is their own desire

00:42:13.960 --> 00:42:16.880
is working, their own power is..."

00:42:17.080 --> 00:42:19.360
So they are so sensitive, I can't understand.

00:42:19.560 --> 00:42:21.360
Seventy per cent of

00:42:21.560 --> 00:42:24.320
Russians are extremely

00:42:24.520 --> 00:42:30.120
sensitive to spirituality - all Eastern bloc.

00:42:30.320 --> 00:42:34.200
We have been busy with our materialism, with our choices this...

00:42:34.400 --> 00:42:38.800
Where have we landed?

00:42:38.960 --> 00:42:40.560
And when they had the coup I was there,

00:42:40.760 --> 00:42:42.240
and I asked, "Aren’t you worried?

00:42:42.440 --> 00:42:44.800
Aren’t you worried about this coup?" They said,

00:42:45.000 --> 00:42:46.600
"Why? Why should we worry?

00:42:46.800 --> 00:42:51.200
We are in the kingdom of God, why should we worry?"

00:42:51.400 --> 00:42:54.400
Simple answer.

00:42:54.600 --> 00:42:56.840
Such lovely people they are!

00:42:57.040 --> 00:42:58.440
They had never known Me, they had

00:42:58.640 --> 00:42:59.800
never seen Me, I mean...

00:42:59.960 --> 00:43:01.880
And no other ‘guru’ could stay there,

00:43:02.080 --> 00:43:04.800
you will be surprised, they threw out all of them.

00:43:04.960 --> 00:43:08.120
So this sensitivity comes I don’t know from where.

00:43:08.320 --> 00:43:10.960
How they have understood that

00:43:11.160 --> 00:43:14.680
reality is the thing we have to achieve now,

00:43:14.880 --> 00:43:19.640
that we have to become the ‘Spirit’, the ‘soul’,

00:43:19.840 --> 00:43:23.560
and not anything else.

00:43:23.760 --> 00:43:30.320
I was amazed the way these people have reacted!

00:43:30.520 --> 00:43:32.960
I don’t want to put a sort of a competition

00:43:33.160 --> 00:43:34.880
for you or a challenge for you.

00:43:35.120 --> 00:43:37.360
But definitely there's something -

00:43:37.560 --> 00:43:41.280
despite their very bad government and everything,

00:43:41.480 --> 00:43:47.880
how they have maintained themselves, so introspective.

00:43:48.080 --> 00:43:50.360
I wish

00:43:50.560 --> 00:43:52.960
people all over the world understand

00:43:53.160 --> 00:43:54.560
that there are problems.

00:43:54.800 --> 00:43:57.000
Your children have problems.

00:43:57.200 --> 00:43:59.040
Other day I was reading that

00:43:59.240 --> 00:44:06.960
you cannot avoid small children, teenage children

00:44:07.160 --> 00:44:11.640
who are not taking drugs.

00:44:11.840 --> 00:44:14.960
Why do they take drugs?

00:44:15.160 --> 00:44:18.640
They are seeking something.

00:44:18.840 --> 00:44:23.440
And they can’t find it - out of frustration.

00:44:23.640 --> 00:44:25.080
But with Sahaja Yoga

00:44:25.280 --> 00:44:28.520
people have given up drugs overnight -

00:44:28.720 --> 00:44:32.320
I assure you - there are some sitting here like that.

00:44:32.520 --> 00:44:34.320
Overnight they gave up drugs

00:44:34.520 --> 00:44:37.320
and whatever damage it had caused them on their brains,

00:44:37.520 --> 00:44:42.040
they have been recovered.

00:44:42.240 --> 00:44:44.360
All these indulgences

00:44:44.560 --> 00:44:47.760
that have suffered,

00:44:47.960 --> 00:44:52.480
because of the genes, I think, genes, must be the [cause]...

00:44:52.680 --> 00:44:55.320
The other day I read about the genes that

00:44:55.520 --> 00:44:58.440
there are two protective genes within us.

00:44:58.640 --> 00:45:00.680
Surprisingly they said

00:45:00.880 --> 00:45:04.880
that Asians have them all the time.

00:45:05.080 --> 00:45:08.080
So they take time to take to something like that.

00:45:08.280 --> 00:45:09.880
One gene

00:45:10.080 --> 00:45:12.960
protects you from being violent, angry,

00:45:13.200 --> 00:45:18.960
hot tempered, cruel

00:45:19.160 --> 00:45:22.960
corrupt, all kinds of things.

00:45:23.160 --> 00:45:27.200
We can call it the father, the sin against the father.

00:45:27.400 --> 00:45:31.160
And the another gene protects you from indulging

00:45:31.400 --> 00:45:34.680
into destructive things: sex,

00:45:34.880 --> 00:45:37.880
too much of it, I mean this all kinds of rapes and so many

00:45:38.080 --> 00:45:40.920
horrible things that we have never heard of such things

00:45:41.120 --> 00:45:42.960
that are going on in these countries,

00:45:43.160 --> 00:45:47.080
where they are supposed to be developed.

00:45:47.280 --> 00:45:49.640
And also indulging into

00:45:49.840 --> 00:45:56.120
drugs and alcohol and all that.

00:45:56.320 --> 00:45:58.520
This protective gene

00:45:58.720 --> 00:46:03.960
is being absolutely awakened again I have seen

00:46:04.160 --> 00:46:05.480
after Realization.

00:46:05.680 --> 00:46:11.400
Whether you are an Asian or not, makes no difference.

00:46:11.600 --> 00:46:13.960
But also look at these Germans.

00:46:14.160 --> 00:46:17.120
They say that they are the highest race, you know they feel.

00:46:17.320 --> 00:46:19.920
They are the ones who killed small little children in the

00:46:20.120 --> 00:46:23.240
gas chamber and they saw them suffering.

00:46:23.440 --> 00:46:26.480
How could they do it?

00:46:26.680 --> 00:46:29.040
And they are supposed to be a very,

00:46:29.240 --> 00:46:31.240
what you call them,

00:46:31.440 --> 00:46:33.840
higher races. Max Muller says

00:46:34.040 --> 00:46:36.440
that they came to India and wrote ‘Vedas’.

00:46:36.640 --> 00:46:40.840
How can they write ‘Vedas’, these people?

00:46:41.040 --> 00:46:43.080
They are not afraid of God,

00:46:43.280 --> 00:46:45.960
the way they have behaved...

00:46:46.200 --> 00:46:49.760
But now Sahaja Yogis, the Sahaja Yogis Germans, you should say,

00:46:49.960 --> 00:46:53.760
the gentlest people you could think of, gentlest.

00:46:53.960 --> 00:46:56.920
They won’t hurt you, I mean, they are so beautiful.

00:46:57.160 --> 00:47:02.680
So this ‘Kundalini’ is the one, She cleanses all that,

00:47:02.880 --> 00:47:09.440
makes you peaceful, joyous and collective.

00:47:09.640 --> 00:47:15.080
Now I hope you all get your Realization tonight.

00:47:15.280 --> 00:47:17.440
Have faith in yourself - that's the main thing.

00:47:17.640 --> 00:47:21.720
You must have faith that you will all get Realization.

00:47:21.920 --> 00:47:25.120
I know there are people who have some questions also.

00:47:25.320 --> 00:47:28.120
These questions now I can answer - for the last

00:47:28.320 --> 00:47:31.040
twenty four years I have been doing this kind of work

00:47:31.240 --> 00:47:32.880
all over the world.

00:47:33.080 --> 00:47:34.080
So I can answer,

00:47:34.280 --> 00:47:37.680
because it's just a mental acrobat - I have become quite an expert.

00:47:37.880 --> 00:47:39.800
But it is of no use.

00:47:40.000 --> 00:47:44.760
By that thing you are not going to get to your Realization.

00:47:44.960 --> 00:47:48.560
What you have to ask really is your Self-Realization.

00:47:48.760 --> 00:47:54.160
This power is the power of pure desire.

00:47:54.360 --> 00:47:58.640
All other desires, as you know, in economics,

00:47:58.840 --> 00:48:02.160
that in general that they are not satiable.

00:48:02.360 --> 00:48:06.360
You may be aware, may not be aware, but this desire is within you,

00:48:06.560 --> 00:48:08.280
is to become the Spirit,

00:48:08.480 --> 00:48:10.880
to become one with this All Pervading Power

00:48:11.080 --> 00:48:14.560
and that acts, works and helps you.

00:48:14.760 --> 00:48:16.560
Everything is tangible.

00:48:16.760 --> 00:48:21.360
You will be amazed how it works,

00:48:21.560 --> 00:48:24.360
how it helps you!

00:48:24.560 --> 00:48:26.320
The second thing I have to tell you

00:48:26.520 --> 00:48:29.120
that it is not an individual thing.

00:48:29.320 --> 00:48:30.920
It is not that, you can say, "Oh!".

00:48:31.120 --> 00:48:32.960
First day you may feel very happy

00:48:33.200 --> 00:48:36.920
and very relaxed, on top of the world.

00:48:37.120 --> 00:48:39.200
That's not important.

00:48:39.400 --> 00:48:41.480
You have to come to the collective.

00:48:41.680 --> 00:48:43.280
You must understand

00:48:43.480 --> 00:48:46.960
the whole knowledge about your internal being

00:48:47.200 --> 00:48:51.720
and you have to be with the collective to grow.

00:48:51.920 --> 00:48:56.120
Like if I take out one, say

00:48:56.320 --> 00:48:59.920
nail out of my fingers, it will never grow.

00:49:00.120 --> 00:49:01.880
So it's the

00:49:02.080 --> 00:49:06.680
whole being, is a living organism.

00:49:06.880 --> 00:49:09.440
Only thing, you have to pay

00:49:09.640 --> 00:49:13.720
some time, as time... for it.

00:49:13.920 --> 00:49:18.000
They will tell you how to be in meditation, not to do meditation,

00:49:18.200 --> 00:49:21.320
how to be in meditation.

00:49:21.520 --> 00:49:24.520
So first you get the state of ‘thoughtless awareness’ -

00:49:24.720 --> 00:49:26.880
we call it as ‘Nirvichar Samadhi’.

00:49:27.080 --> 00:49:30.800
And then the state you get is called as ‘Nirvikalpa Samadhi’,

00:49:30.960 --> 00:49:34.040
where you get all the powers of raising others' ‘Kundalini’,

00:49:34.240 --> 00:49:36.960
giving them Realization, curing, everything.

00:49:37.200 --> 00:49:39.640
Those who have never come to the stage become orators.

00:49:39.840 --> 00:49:42.800
See these musicians singing Indian songs.

00:49:43.000 --> 00:49:44.880
Can you imagine this?

00:49:45.080 --> 00:49:48.080
I mean, English speaking people, so hard

00:49:48.280 --> 00:49:50.560
for Indian music, I tell you,

00:49:50.760 --> 00:49:53.080
especially for Indian words.

00:49:53.280 --> 00:49:54.800
But when they sing, ask Indians,

00:49:55.000 --> 00:49:57.640
they will tell you they sing like Indians...

00:49:57.840 --> 00:50:00.440
It was so difficult to teach even one word

00:50:00.640 --> 00:50:02.320
to the Englishmen in India -

00:50:02.520 --> 00:50:06.800
one word. And now you see this.

00:50:06.960 --> 00:50:08.440
What has happened to them?

00:50:08.640 --> 00:50:10.120
How suddenly they have picked up

00:50:10.320 --> 00:50:16.520
all the rhythm, all the thing, which is very difficult.

00:50:16.720 --> 00:50:18.560
So...

00:50:18.760 --> 00:50:20.800
all these powers which are within you,

00:50:20.960 --> 00:50:22.960
you have to manifest

00:50:23.160 --> 00:50:27.360
and enjoy your virtues, enjoy your virtues.

00:50:27.560 --> 00:50:31.320
You don’t become proud, but you enjoy them.

00:50:31.520 --> 00:50:33.560
You enjoy your generosity,

00:50:33.760 --> 00:50:35.680
enjoy your compassion,

00:50:35.880 --> 00:50:39.960
never feel that you are

00:50:40.200 --> 00:50:43.400
taking too much trouble, you are doing this and that, nothing.

00:50:43.600 --> 00:50:47.160
You think of others all the time and you live in peace

00:50:47.360 --> 00:50:49.440
and create peace all around.

00:50:49.640 --> 00:50:53.000
We have these people from sixty

00:50:53.200 --> 00:50:56.680
nations; they come to India once a year.

00:50:56.880 --> 00:51:01.200
I've never seen them quarrelling, fighting,

00:51:01.400 --> 00:51:05.840
doing anything against each other - never.

00:51:06.040 --> 00:51:10.040
How do they live from all different countries, from Chinese

00:51:10.240 --> 00:51:13.880
to Africans, from Africans to English

00:51:14.080 --> 00:51:18.200
and from English to Americans and Australians - so many?

00:51:18.400 --> 00:51:20.880
In Sydney we have twenty two centers.

00:51:21.080 --> 00:51:24.560
I must say Australia is one of our

00:51:24.760 --> 00:51:28.320
very great country which has really

00:51:28.520 --> 00:51:35.480
very enthusiastically has taken to Sahaja Yoga.

00:51:35.680 --> 00:51:38.600
And I am sure also you all will.

00:51:38.800 --> 00:51:42.280
We have a great story in our ‘Puranas’ about Australia

00:51:42.480 --> 00:51:44.840
which sometimes I'll tell you.

00:51:45.040 --> 00:51:47.080
So may God Bless you!

00:51:47.280 --> 00:51:52.600
And you be confident that you will have your Realization just now.

00:51:52.800 --> 00:51:57.280
You don’t have to do much - just it will take ten minutes more.

00:52:03.160 --> 00:52:06.320
But, of course, I respect your freedom.

00:52:06.520 --> 00:52:08.360
If you don’t want to have your Realization,

00:52:08.560 --> 00:52:11.480
you should leave the hall. I cannot force on you.

00:52:11.680 --> 00:52:13.960
It is something it cannot be forced.

00:52:14.160 --> 00:52:16.800
I respect your freedom out and out.

00:52:17.000 --> 00:52:20.200
So, if you want to go, you can go.

00:52:29.720 --> 00:52:34.120
All of you want Realization - it's very good.

00:52:38.160 --> 00:52:39.960
Now one thing that should not upset you,

00:52:40.160 --> 00:52:42.320
because I've seen people get upset if I tell them

00:52:42.520 --> 00:52:44.040
that you have to take out your shoes.

00:52:44.240 --> 00:52:47.480
I hope you won’t be upset with that.

00:52:53.040 --> 00:52:59.000
You need not take out your socks but your shoes.

00:52:59.200 --> 00:53:01.200
I does, sometimes.

00:53:16.120 --> 00:53:18.800
Don’t have to say any mantras, nothing,

00:53:19.040 --> 00:53:20.960
and you don’t have to concentrate also.

00:53:21.160 --> 00:53:24.440
Please don’t try to concentrate.

00:53:24.640 --> 00:53:27.800
Just keep yourself open.

00:53:27.960 --> 00:53:30.720
Don’t force yourself into anything.

00:53:30.920 --> 00:53:33.080
As I am saying, telling you that

00:53:33.280 --> 00:53:35.800
it has become so easy now -

00:53:36.000 --> 00:53:37.360
you don’t have to go to Himalayas

00:53:37.560 --> 00:53:39.960
and stand on your head or anything.

00:53:40.160 --> 00:53:42.400
You have to be very comfortable

00:53:42.600 --> 00:53:45.640
and also

00:53:45.840 --> 00:53:50.760
you should be very much pleasantly placed toward yourself.

00:53:50.960 --> 00:53:53.520
Because as I said, you are human beings,

00:53:53.720 --> 00:53:56.960
you are at the epitomy of evolution.

00:53:57.160 --> 00:54:01.880
And you are...  have a right to have this,

00:54:02.080 --> 00:54:07.240
because you are born at this time with a special purpose.

00:54:07.440 --> 00:54:09.600
So in no way you should condemn yourself.

00:54:09.800 --> 00:54:11.800
This is the first condition.

00:54:11.960 --> 00:54:16.680
Have full confidence.

00:54:16.880 --> 00:54:20.040
The another thing is you shouldn’t feel guilty at this time;

00:54:20.240 --> 00:54:22.600
please don’t feel guilty for anything.

00:54:22.800 --> 00:54:26.840
It has become a fashion now to feel guilty for anything.

00:54:27.040 --> 00:54:29.640
I mean, even, if supposing you spill some

00:54:29.840 --> 00:54:32.520
coffee you go on feeling guilty for your life.

00:54:32.720 --> 00:54:34.960
What's this going on?

00:54:35.160 --> 00:54:37.120
You must value yourself.

00:54:37.320 --> 00:54:39.360
This life is not meant

00:54:39.560 --> 00:54:42.880
for feeling bad for small, small things.

00:54:43.080 --> 00:54:47.160
It is very great, it’s very precious.

00:54:47.360 --> 00:54:48.920
So please don’t have any guilt.

00:54:49.120 --> 00:54:52.600
But if you have, then you catch on this center here.

00:54:52.800 --> 00:54:59.400
And this is such a dangerous thing because it gives you

00:54:59.600 --> 00:55:02.600
what we call as angina.

00:55:02.800 --> 00:55:07.840
It may give you spondylitis. It may give you very lethargic organs.

00:55:08.040 --> 00:55:10.480
So very dangerous is to feel guilt.

00:55:10.680 --> 00:55:12.800
So why feel guilty unnecessarily?

00:55:12.960 --> 00:55:16.520
I tell you if you were guilty, you would have been in jail.

00:55:16.720 --> 00:55:20.360
Now you are sitting here, so don’t feel guilty about

00:55:20.560 --> 00:55:22.320
anything whatsoever.

00:55:22.520 --> 00:55:26.640
I assure you, you are not guilty.

00:55:26.840 --> 00:55:34.120
So, you have to really forgive yourself.

00:55:34.320 --> 00:55:39.880
Now, the most simple condition is this

00:55:40.080 --> 00:55:44.360
that you have to forgive everyone.

00:55:44.560 --> 00:55:47.600
People might say it's very difficult to forgive.

00:55:47.800 --> 00:55:51.160
But, whether you forgive or not - I am telling the logic,

00:55:51.360 --> 00:55:54.600
now think about it - whether you forgive or not what do you do?

00:55:54.840 --> 00:55:57.280
I don’t do anything.

00:55:57.480 --> 00:56:01.520
But when you don’t forgive, then you play into wrong hands.

00:56:01.720 --> 00:56:06.440
Those who have troubled you, tortured you,

00:56:06.640 --> 00:56:08.000
are not feeling bad.

00:56:08.200 --> 00:56:11.960
But you are the one who is torturing yourself.

00:56:12.160 --> 00:56:15.760
But at this time, the problem is that this centre of Agnya

00:56:15.960 --> 00:56:21.080
which is like this, absolutely constructed like this, like a cross -

00:56:21.280 --> 00:56:23.560
it is on the optic chiasma -

00:56:23.760 --> 00:56:26.200
and if you don’t forgive, it won’t open at all.

00:56:26.400 --> 00:56:27.400
But if you forgive

00:56:27.600 --> 00:56:30.440
it will definitely open and the Kundalini will pass.

00:56:30.640 --> 00:56:33.960
So, at this juncture you as it is

00:56:34.200 --> 00:56:35.640
troubled yourself so much,

00:56:35.840 --> 00:56:37.880
at this juncture please,

00:56:38.080 --> 00:56:41.120
please forgive everyone in general.

00:56:41.320 --> 00:56:44.640
Don’t even think about them because it is a headache.

00:56:44.840 --> 00:56:47.680
It's a real headache even to think of these people.

00:56:47.880 --> 00:56:49.960
So you just forgive in general.

00:56:50.200 --> 00:56:54.320
Of course we'll tell you how to do it. It's very simple.

00:56:54.520 --> 00:56:58.120
Now to begin with you keep your eyes open,

00:56:58.320 --> 00:57:01.400
I'll show you how you have to

00:57:01.600 --> 00:57:08.040
yourself enrich your own centers - very simple.

