You have to be comfortable. That’s very important.

00:57:13.960 --> 00:57:15.920
Please both the feet apart from each other

00:57:16.120 --> 00:57:18.680
because these are two powers, left and right.

00:57:18.880 --> 00:57:22.880
Put your left hand towards Me on your lap,

00:57:23.080 --> 00:57:25.960
just like this.

00:57:26.200 --> 00:57:28.800
And now

00:57:28.960 --> 00:57:34.280
we have to use our left side with our right hand.

00:57:34.480 --> 00:57:39.920
Now please put your right hand on your heart.

00:57:40.120 --> 00:57:46.880
This is the center where the Spirit resides.

00:57:47.080 --> 00:57:48.680
If you become the Spirit,

00:57:48.880 --> 00:57:52.120
you become your own master in the light of the Spirit.

00:57:52.320 --> 00:57:54.640
So please take your right hand

00:57:54.880 --> 00:57:59.320
in the upper portion of your abdomen, on the liver.

00:57:59.520 --> 00:58:05.840
All of you should do it, please.

00:58:06.040 --> 00:58:08.400
This is the center of your mastery

00:58:08.640 --> 00:58:11.960
which is created by great prophets

00:58:12.160 --> 00:58:18.240
and seers and sages.

00:58:18.440 --> 00:58:21.720
Surprisingly the center of pure knowledge

00:58:21.920 --> 00:58:25.280
is lower here on the left hand side

00:58:25.480 --> 00:58:31.240
in the lower portion of your abdomen on the left hand side.

00:58:31.440 --> 00:58:38.840
Whatever you have done, forget it, forget it.

00:58:39.040 --> 00:58:45.680
Now raise your right hand in the upper portion of your abdomen.

00:58:45.880 --> 00:58:52.040
Now on your heart.

00:58:52.240 --> 00:58:55.960
Now in the corner of your neck and shoulders.

00:58:56.160 --> 00:58:57.720
As I have already told you

00:58:57.920 --> 00:58:59.920
when this center catches what is the problem.

00:59:00.120 --> 00:59:06.440
Turn your head to your right, please.

00:59:06.640 --> 00:59:09.120
It’s very catching today.

00:59:09.320 --> 00:59:14.520
Please don’t feel guilty for anything. You must...

00:59:14.720 --> 00:59:19.760
There.

00:59:19.960 --> 00:59:23.360
Please take your right hand on top of your forehead across

00:59:23.560 --> 00:59:26.960
and bend your head slowly.

00:59:27.160 --> 00:59:31.440
We have to be humble about it, you see.

00:59:31.640 --> 00:59:38.320
So here you have to forgive everyone in general.

00:59:41.040 --> 00:59:46.120
Now take back your right hand on the backside of your head

00:59:46.320 --> 00:59:49.840
and push back your head as far as possible.

00:59:50.040 --> 00:59:54.880
Here,

00:59:55.080 --> 00:59:59.040
without counting your mistakes,

00:59:59.240 --> 01:00:02.680
without feeling guilty, just for your satisfaction,

01:00:02.880 --> 01:00:05.240
you will have to ask forgiveness

01:00:05.440 --> 01:00:11.520
from this All Pervading Power.

01:00:11.720 --> 01:00:16.640
Now please stretch your hand or palm fully.

01:00:16.840 --> 01:00:19.440
Now we go to the last center,

01:00:19.640 --> 01:00:22.040
so please put the centre of your palm

01:00:22.240 --> 01:00:25.360
on top of the fontanel bone area

01:00:25.560 --> 01:00:30.400
which was a soft bone in your childhood.

01:00:30.600 --> 01:00:35.160
Now please put down your head.

01:00:35.360 --> 01:00:37.120
Now push back your fingers nicely

01:00:37.320 --> 01:00:42.320
so there's a good pressure on your scalp.

01:00:42.520 --> 01:00:46.360
Now put down your head and you have to move, move the scalp

01:00:46.600 --> 01:00:51.080
seven times clockwise very slowly.

01:01:02.600 --> 01:01:05.200
That’s all we have to do actually.

01:01:05.400 --> 01:01:07.960
But remember you have to push back your fingers.

01:01:08.200 --> 01:01:11.160
Now you can take out your spectacles

01:01:11.360 --> 01:01:13.240
because you have to close your eyes.

01:01:13.440 --> 01:01:16.320
It might help also your eyesight.

01:01:16.520 --> 01:01:19.680
Please,

01:01:19.920 --> 01:01:21.920
before closing I must tell you again

01:01:22.120 --> 01:01:23.920
that please put both the

01:01:24.120 --> 01:01:26.560
legs apart from each other

01:01:26.760 --> 01:01:30.440
and the left hand

01:01:30.640 --> 01:01:36.840
towards Me on your lap comfortably in any way that you like.

01:01:37.040 --> 01:01:41.840
And then now place your right hand on your heart.

01:01:45.440 --> 01:01:49.320
Here, I've told you resides the Spirit.

01:01:49.520 --> 01:01:52.400
You have to ask Me

01:01:52.600 --> 01:01:56.880
a very fundamental question about yourself in your heart.

01:01:57.080 --> 01:02:02.400
So please,

01:02:02.600 --> 01:02:06.440
ask in your heart, three times.

01:02:06.640 --> 01:02:10.480
You can call me ‘Mother’ or ‘Shri Mataji’ whatever you like.

01:02:10.680 --> 01:02:13.880
“Mother, am I the Spirit?”

01:02:14.080 --> 01:02:15.960
Ask this question three times in your heart.

01:02:16.200 --> 01:02:20.280
"Mother, am I the Spirit?"

01:02:31.240 --> 01:02:33.760
Now, I've told you if you become the ‘Spirit’,

01:02:33.960 --> 01:02:37.480
you become your own master.

01:02:37.680 --> 01:02:39.680
So now take down your right hand

01:02:39.880 --> 01:02:41.880
in the upper portion of your abdomen

01:02:42.080 --> 01:02:44.840
on the left hand side.

01:02:46.080 --> 01:02:50.400
Here,

01:02:50.600 --> 01:02:53.520
you have to ask another fundamental question.

01:02:53.720 --> 01:02:59.960
“Mother, am I my master?”

01:03:00.200 --> 01:03:05.200
Ask this question three times.

01:03:09.560 --> 01:03:12.720
I have already told you

01:03:12.920 --> 01:03:16.280
that I respect your freedom.

01:03:16.480 --> 01:03:18.640
And I cannot force

01:03:18.840 --> 01:03:24.240
divine pure knowledge on you.

01:03:24.440 --> 01:03:25.920
So now

01:03:26.160 --> 01:03:27.960
please take your right hand

01:03:28.160 --> 01:03:33.040
in the lower portion of your abdomen on the left hand side.

01:03:33.240 --> 01:03:40.160
Here,

01:03:40.400 --> 01:03:42.600
you have to ask six times,

01:03:42.800 --> 01:03:46.840
because this center has got six petals,

01:03:47.040 --> 01:03:53.800
“Mother, please give me pure knowledge”,

01:03:53.960 --> 01:03:59.320
or you can say, “Mother please give me divine pure knowledge”.

01:03:59.520 --> 01:04:04.920
Whatever is divine is pure.

01:04:05.120 --> 01:04:07.680
Six times.

01:04:07.880 --> 01:04:10.800
As soon as you start asking

01:04:11.000 --> 01:04:13.080
for pure divine knowledge,

01:04:13.280 --> 01:04:17.840
the ‘Kundalini’ starts rising like a primule.

01:04:18.040 --> 01:04:23.160
Now we have to

01:04:23.360 --> 01:04:26.840
open our higher centers

01:04:27.040 --> 01:04:31.600
by our self-confidence,

01:04:31.800 --> 01:04:34.240
for the Kundalini to pass through.

01:04:34.440 --> 01:04:36.680
Now, take your right hand -

01:04:36.880 --> 01:04:39.080
you are working only on the left hand side -

01:04:39.280 --> 01:04:40.360
in the upper portion

01:04:40.560 --> 01:04:42.600
of your abdomen, on the left hand side.

01:04:42.800 --> 01:04:45.280
Press it hard.

01:04:45.480 --> 01:04:52.440
Now, here with full confidence, please say ten times,

01:04:52.640 --> 01:04:56.040
“Mother, I am my own master”.

01:04:56.240 --> 01:04:58.080
The Kundalini wants

01:04:58.280 --> 01:05:01.960
you to show yourself confidence.

01:05:07.200 --> 01:05:11.960
Please say it ten times.

01:05:12.160 --> 01:05:14.760
At the very outset, I've told you

01:05:14.960 --> 01:05:17.600
that the truth is that you are not this body,

01:05:17.800 --> 01:05:20.240
this mind, this ego, these feelings,

01:05:20.440 --> 01:05:23.240
these emotions, these conditionings,

01:05:23.440 --> 01:05:30.800
but you are the pure Spirit.

01:05:30.960 --> 01:05:35.440
So, now raise your right hand on top of your heart.

01:05:35.640 --> 01:05:40.480
And here you have to say again with full self-confidence,

01:05:40.680 --> 01:05:45.120
“Mother, I am the pure Spirit”.

01:05:45.320 --> 01:05:46.720
Please say it.

01:05:46.920 --> 01:05:49.160
Please say it twelve times,

01:05:49.360 --> 01:05:54.520
“Mother I am the pure Spirit”.

01:05:59.000 --> 01:06:00.920
I have already told you

01:06:01.160 --> 01:06:04.560
that this All Pervading Power

01:06:04.760 --> 01:06:08.280
is the ocean of knowledge,

01:06:08.480 --> 01:06:10.480
ocean of compassion,

01:06:10.680 --> 01:06:16.080
ocean of blessings, but above all it is the ocean of forgiveness.

01:06:16.280 --> 01:06:20.160
And whatever mistakes you might have committed,

01:06:20.360 --> 01:06:24.320
are easily dissolved by this ocean of forgiveness.

01:06:24.520 --> 01:06:26.200
So forgive yourself.

01:06:26.400 --> 01:06:27.720
And put your right hand

01:06:27.920 --> 01:06:30.480
in the corner of your neck and shoulder

01:06:30.680 --> 01:06:34.560
and turn your head to your right.

01:06:34.800 --> 01:06:36.880
Here,

01:06:37.080 --> 01:06:39.280
with full confidence again,

01:06:39.480 --> 01:06:43.120
you have to say sixteen times,

01:06:43.320 --> 01:06:46.800
“Mother, I am not guilty at all”,

01:06:47.000 --> 01:06:50.440
“Mother I am not guilty at all”. Please say this.

01:06:50.640 --> 01:06:52.560
Is very important because this center

01:06:52.760 --> 01:06:57.640
is catching very much tonight here.

01:07:07.040 --> 01:07:08.760
Now I have told you

01:07:08.960 --> 01:07:12.240
whether you forgive or you don’t forgive, you don’t do anything.

01:07:12.440 --> 01:07:14.080
But if you don’t forgive,

01:07:14.280 --> 01:07:16.560
then you play into wrong hands

01:07:16.760 --> 01:07:18.120
and torture yourself.

01:07:18.320 --> 01:07:21.920
Especially at this moment, you should forgive

01:07:22.120 --> 01:07:25.960
all of them, without thinking about them, in general,

01:07:26.160 --> 01:07:29.520
so that your center opens out.

01:07:29.720 --> 01:07:33.840
Otherwise at this important moment,

01:07:34.040 --> 01:07:36.680
you may miss your Self Realization.

01:07:36.880 --> 01:07:38.360
It's very important

01:07:38.560 --> 01:07:42.560
to forgive all of them from your heart.

01:07:42.760 --> 01:07:46.000
Not how many times, it's not the point, from your heart.

01:07:46.200 --> 01:07:47.840
So now please put your right hand

01:07:48.040 --> 01:07:49.800
on you forehead across

01:07:50.000 --> 01:07:56.080
and bend your head as much as you can.

01:07:56.280 --> 01:07:59.720
And here,

01:07:59.920 --> 01:08:04.000
you have to say,

01:08:04.200 --> 01:08:09.400
not how many times, but from your heart,

01:08:09.600 --> 01:08:15.840
“Mother, I forgive everyone in general”,

01:08:16.040 --> 01:08:19.960
from your heart. Please say it from your heart.

01:08:34.040 --> 01:08:35.520
And now

01:08:35.720 --> 01:08:39.040
please put your right hand on the back side of your head

01:08:39.240 --> 01:08:46.800
and push back your head as far as possible.

01:08:47.000 --> 01:08:49.160
Here, without feeling guilty,

01:08:49.360 --> 01:08:51.120
without counting your mistakes,

01:08:51.320 --> 01:08:54.200
just for your satisfaction,

01:08:54.400 --> 01:08:55.480
you have to say,

01:08:55.680 --> 01:09:00.520
not how many times, but from your heart,

01:09:00.720 --> 01:09:02.560
“Oh, Divine Power,

01:09:02.760 --> 01:09:07.640
if I have done any mistake,

01:09:07.840 --> 01:09:11.720
knowingly or unknowingly, please forgive me”.

01:09:11.920 --> 01:09:13.920
Just say it from your heart.

01:09:14.120 --> 01:09:15.640
“O Divine Power,

01:09:15.800 --> 01:09:19.480
if I have done anything wrong,

01:09:19.680 --> 01:09:24.400
knowingly or unknowingly, please forgive me”.

01:09:32.560 --> 01:09:34.680
Now

01:09:34.880 --> 01:09:38.760
please stretch your palms.

01:09:38.960 --> 01:09:40.760
Put the center of your palm

01:09:40.960 --> 01:09:44.200
on top of your fontanel bone area

01:09:44.400 --> 01:09:48.520
which is a soft bone in your childhood.

01:09:48.720 --> 01:09:50.040
Here again,

01:09:50.240 --> 01:09:54.320
I cannot force Self-Realization on you. You have to ask for it.

01:09:54.520 --> 01:09:57.280
So now push back your fingers - that's important -

01:09:57.480 --> 01:10:00.240
and please put down your head.

01:10:00.480 --> 01:10:03.400
Now move your scalp with this pressure,

01:10:03.600 --> 01:10:06.280
seven times, saying

01:10:06.480 --> 01:10:07.880
seven times,

01:10:08.080 --> 01:10:12.920
“Mother, please give me my Self-Realization”,

01:10:13.120 --> 01:10:15.640
because I cannot force it on you.

01:10:19.760 --> 01:10:21.800
Please push back your fingers.

01:10:22.000 --> 01:10:26.480
Bend your heads; please push back your fingers.

01:10:30.160 --> 01:10:32.000
Keep your eyes shut, till I tell you

01:10:32.200 --> 01:10:34.480
please keep them shut.

01:11:03.920 --> 01:11:07.160
Please take down your hands

01:11:07.360 --> 01:11:12.000
and try to open your eyes slowly.

01:11:12.200 --> 01:11:16.440
Push both the hands towards Me.

01:11:21.840 --> 01:11:22.880
Now,

01:11:23.120 --> 01:11:26.360
put the left hand towards Me like this,

01:11:26.560 --> 01:11:30.200
bend your head and see with the right hand

01:11:30.400 --> 01:11:36.480
if there is a cool or a warm breeze-like energy

01:11:36.680 --> 01:11:39.960
is coming out of your fontanel bone area.

01:11:40.200 --> 01:11:43.920
Now don’t doubt, because air conditioning is not in your head.

01:11:44.120 --> 01:11:48.560
So just see for yourself. Some people think it is air conditioning.

01:11:51.680 --> 01:11:54.040
Some people get it hot.

01:11:54.240 --> 01:11:56.320
Some people get it far,

01:11:56.520 --> 01:11:57.560
some closer,

01:11:57.760 --> 01:12:00.800
but don’t put your hand on top of your head,

01:12:01.000 --> 01:12:02.280
away from it.

01:12:02.480 --> 01:12:03.840
See for yourself,

01:12:04.040 --> 01:12:07.240
and if it is hot, that means you have not yet forgiven.

01:12:07.440 --> 01:12:09.480
So please forgive also.

01:12:09.680 --> 01:12:11.120
Now,

01:12:11.320 --> 01:12:14.280
please put your right hand. Now, bend your head nicely

01:12:14.480 --> 01:12:17.120
and see for yourself with the left hand

01:12:17.320 --> 01:12:23.320
if there's a cool or a hot breeze-like energy is coming

01:12:23.520 --> 01:12:28.560
out of your fontanel bone area.

01:12:28.760 --> 01:12:33.640
You have to move your hand up and down, sideways also. All right.

01:12:33.840 --> 01:12:38.080
Now do it with the left hand again.

01:12:42.560 --> 01:12:44.640
Little further. Some people get it further.

01:12:44.840 --> 01:12:50.160
Bend your heads, that is important, bend your heads.

01:12:51.960 --> 01:12:54.760
Now,

01:12:54.960 --> 01:12:59.040
please put both your hands towards the sky.

01:12:59.240 --> 01:13:01.080
Push back your head

01:13:01.280 --> 01:13:04.040
and ask anyone of these three questions,

01:13:04.240 --> 01:13:06.840
three times, anyone of them.

01:13:07.040 --> 01:13:08.960
You can say, ”Mother,

01:13:09.160 --> 01:13:13.040
is this the cool breeze of the Holy Ghost?”,

01:13:13.240 --> 01:13:16.000
or ”Mother, is this the

01:13:16.200 --> 01:13:19.920
All Pervading Power of Divine Love?”,

01:13:20.120 --> 01:13:24.160
or ”Mother, is this the Ruh

01:13:24.360 --> 01:13:25.560
or Paramchaitanya?”.

01:13:25.760 --> 01:13:29.360
Ask anyone of these questions, three times.

01:13:35.920 --> 01:13:39.720
Now, just come down.

01:13:43.840 --> 01:13:46.680
Now please put your hands like this

01:13:46.880 --> 01:13:50.120
and watch Me without thinking.

01:13:50.320 --> 01:13:53.840
Just watch Me without thinking.

01:14:04.680 --> 01:14:07.680
All those who have felt

01:14:07.880 --> 01:14:11.480
hot or cold breeze on their fingertips,

01:14:11.680 --> 01:14:17.720
on their palms or out of their fontanel bone area,

01:14:17.920 --> 01:14:20.080
please raise both your hands.

01:14:22.480 --> 01:14:25.960
My God! Look at that.

01:14:26.200 --> 01:14:28.480
I mean most of you.

01:14:28.680 --> 01:14:29.840
May God bless you!

01:14:30.040 --> 01:14:31.520
It's tremendous.

01:14:31.720 --> 01:14:34.160
Some didn’t get it, very few,

01:14:34.360 --> 01:14:36.840
but most of you have got it.

01:14:37.040 --> 01:14:39.960
In any case all of you should get it.

01:14:40.160 --> 01:14:42.200
And those who haven’t got

01:14:42.400 --> 01:14:46.280
should please later on come to the stage and they will do it.

01:14:46.480 --> 01:14:47.760
But in the meanwhile

01:14:47.960 --> 01:14:49.560
we'll try something else

01:14:49.760 --> 01:14:52.440
for Realization

01:14:52.640 --> 01:14:55.080
and maybe that might help a little bit.

01:14:55.280 --> 01:14:57.960
[Marathi].

01:14:58.160 --> 01:15:01.880
See this might help.

01:15:06.440 --> 01:15:09.360
This will be only five minutes experiment. Let's see.

01:15:09.560 --> 01:15:12.280
Which song will you sing?

01:15:12.480 --> 01:15:14.480
[Marathi].

01:15:17.360 --> 01:15:20.560
[Marathi].

01:15:20.760 --> 01:15:22.960
This is the song they are going to sing,

01:15:23.160 --> 01:15:26.120
was written - Namadeva -

01:15:26.320 --> 01:15:28.760
by Namadeva in the sixteenth century

01:15:28.960 --> 01:15:31.760
who went then to Punjab

01:15:31.960 --> 01:15:34.760
and Guru Nanak Sahib, you see,

01:15:34.960 --> 01:15:38.600
knew who he was and He asked him to write

01:15:38.800 --> 01:15:41.120
poems in Punjabi language.

01:15:41.320 --> 01:15:45.000
And he has done such big compilation, I know that.

01:15:45.240 --> 01:15:47.480
This guru

01:15:47.680 --> 01:15:48.960
was ...

01:15:49.160 --> 01:15:51.240
he was just a tailor.

01:15:51.440 --> 01:15:53.520
And he went to see, meet

01:15:53.720 --> 01:15:57.960
another realized soul who was a potter.

01:16:00.560 --> 01:16:04.320
And when he went and saw the potter kneading

01:16:04.520 --> 01:16:11.920
the clay with his feet, he just stood there, watching him.

01:16:12.120 --> 01:16:14.880
The potter’s name was Gora Kumbhar.

01:16:15.080 --> 01:16:19.120
Looked at him and what does he say,

01:16:19.320 --> 01:16:22.880
in Marathi says that, but meaning

01:16:23.080 --> 01:16:27.000
that, I came to see here

01:16:27.200 --> 01:16:28.960
the "formless",

01:16:29.200 --> 01:16:32.120
but it is "in the form".

01:16:32.320 --> 01:16:34.120
I see it "in the form".

01:16:34.320 --> 01:16:40.880
I mean only a saint can say it to another saint.

01:16:41.080 --> 01:16:42.440
That’s what happened

01:16:42.640 --> 01:16:46.080
that he went up to Punjab

01:16:46.280 --> 01:16:49.360
where Guru Nanak Sahib

01:16:49.560 --> 01:16:53.560
called him, looked after him and asked him and they made beautiful,

01:16:53.760 --> 01:16:58.040
I mean such beautiful songs there are and they are in Granth Sahib.

01:16:58.240 --> 01:17:01.800
They are all in Granth Sahib.

01:17:03.400 --> 01:17:04.680
[unclear].

01:17:04.880 --> 01:17:06.320
This is the folk song

01:17:06.520 --> 01:17:11.240
which was written, which says, “Oh, Mother, give me my Realization.

01:17:11.440 --> 01:17:14.440
‘Jogwa’ means Yoga - "Please give me that".

01:17:14.640 --> 01:17:15.960
All that they sang,

01:17:16.200 --> 01:17:18.320
all the time they have been singing, even now,

01:17:18.520 --> 01:17:20.360
but they don’t know what it is.

01:17:20.560 --> 01:17:23.280
And they are saying, "Oh, Ambe" - means the Kundalini -

01:17:23.480 --> 01:17:25.280
"please rise, rise".

01:17:25.480 --> 01:17:29.280
And with you can also clap. It will help a lot, I am sure.

01:17:29.480 --> 01:17:34.000
This will definitely consolidate your Self-Realization.

01:17:38.920 --> 01:17:42.400
It is a village song. It’s a rustic...

01:26:27.500 --> 01:26:31.160
Now you feel. Just try to feel now. Let's see.

01:26:31.360 --> 01:26:35.600
You must be feeling more, just see.

01:26:35.800 --> 01:26:37.120
All right?

01:26:37.320 --> 01:26:39.960
Now again, let us see how many of you have really

01:26:40.160 --> 01:26:42.400
felt on your finger tips

01:26:42.600 --> 01:26:47.160
